options(repr.plot.width=5, repr.plot.height=12)
bipart_plot <- ggplot(dat,aes(EpiVal,value))+
                geom_violin(trim = FALSE,aes(group=EpiVal),alpha=0.8)+
                geom_boxplot(width=.1,outlier.color=NA,fill='white')+
                facet_grid(vars(variable_fac),vars(EpiState),scales='free',switch='y')+
                a+ylab('')+ xlab('')+
                stat_compare_means(aes(group=EpiVal,label = paste0("p = ", ..p.format..)),
                       label.x.npc=0.2, label.y.npc=1,size=3.5,family="Times New Roman")+
                theme_bw(base_size=20)+
                theme(legend.position='none',legend.title=element_blank(),
                      legend.text=element_text(margin = margin(r = 5, unit = "pt"),size=12),
                      panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
                      text=element_text( family="Times New Roman"))+
                aes(fill = Color)

options(repr.plot.width=5, repr.plot.height=10)
onet_plot <- ggplot(onet_data,aes(EpiVal,value))+
                geom_boxplot(width=.5,aes(group=EpiVal),alpha=0.7,outlier.shape=NA) + 
                geom_quasirandom(method="tukeyDense")+
                stat_compare_means(aes(group=EpiVal,label = paste0("p = ", ..p.format..)),
                                   label.x.npc=0.26, label.y.npc='top',size=4,family="Times New Roman")+
                facet_grid(vars(variable_fac),vars(EpiVar),scales='free',switch='y')+
                a+ylab('')+xlab('')+
                theme_bw(base_size=20)+
                theme(legend.position='none',legend.title=element_blank(),
                      legend.text=element_text(margin = margin(r = 5, unit = "pt"),size=12),
                      panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
                      text=element_text( family="Times New Roman"))+
                aes(fill = as.factor(Color))

row2 <- arrangeGrob(gephi1,gephi,onet_species,nrow=3,heights=c(1/3,1/3,1/3))

figure4 <- as_ggplot(arrangeGrob(bipart_plot,row2,onet_plot,
            ncol=3,widths=c(1/3,5/12,4/12)))+                                
       draw_plot_label(
        label = c("a", "b", "c",'d',"e","f","g","h","i"), size = 25,
        x = c(0,0,0,0.33,0.33,0.33,0.67,0.67,0.67), 
        y = c(1,0.67,0.33,1,0.67,0.33,1,0.67,0.33),family="Times New Roman")
